snippet.title: Hollow Knight - Retail Release - Skybound Games
snippet.description:
Enter the epic 2D action-adventure world of Hollow Knight and discover new wonders hidden off the beaten path - coming to retail stores in Spring 2019!

Developed by Team Cherry
